message.body: Hey there - how was the weekend with the family?
It was fun thanks for asking. Glad it's over! I didn't get nearly enough work done and school is kicking many ass. How was your weekend?
Might be the first time I hear glad it's over about a weekend! Mine was relaxing, low key for once. How's the rest of your week looking?
might be going dancing Friday ... Care to join?
Well that's right up my alley, keep me posted!
Do you know la boom, or something, in j.p.?
Haven't been, but pretty keen to venture outside my narrow Boston-centric view, sounds like you know the hot spots ha
